";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mati1000\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/652ff3b9594033ddb9b827f51aae26f6?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:13:\"Mati Horovitz\";}s:6:\"pojosh\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:37:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pojosh\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/75b01acab5921ca64af0d307c1f2065a?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:6:\"pojosh\";}s:10:\"bainternet\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:41:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bainternet\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1cdd42c841a307d7460954942e71877e?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:10:\"Bainternet\";}}s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"5.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:3:\"5.4\";s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.6\";s:6:\"rating\";i:96;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:4836;i:4;i:148;i:3;i:51;i:2;i:33;i:1;i:114;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:5182;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:263;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:29;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:4000000;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2020-04-21 3:22pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2016-05-30\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:87:\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-plugins&utm_campaign=plugin-uri&utm_medium=wp-dash\";s:8:\"sections\";a:6:{s:11:\"description\";s:16158:\"<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/kB4U67tiQLA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n<p>Il est temps d’utiliser un constructeur de page en direct, sans aucune limite de conception. Un constructeur de pages qui offre des conceptions de page haut de gamme et des fonctionnalités avancées, jamais vues sur WordPress.</p>\n<p>It&rsquo;s time for <strong><a href=\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Page Builder</a></strong>.</p>\n<h4>Plus rapide. Bien plus rapide.</h4>\n<p>Instant reaction was a key feature we wanted to achieve. And we did. Instant drag &amp; drop page builder, instant live edit, instant page load. The speed of Elementor is not matched by any other page builder, free or paid. This makes the interface fun and easy to work with, as well as reduces the time it takes to design.</p>\n<h4>Conception en direct. Réellement en direct.</h4>\n<p>Never again work on the backend and guess what the frontend will look like. With Elementor page builder, you edit the page and simultaneously see exactly how it looks like. Elementor features live design &amp; inline editing, so the whole process of writing and designing is done directly on the page, with no need to press update or go to preview mode. It also works perfectly with or without Gutenberg.</p>\n<h4>Des surprises que vous ne verrez nulle part ailleurs.</h4>\n<p>With Elementor&rsquo;s unique features, you can create websites that have that certain &lsquo;designer touch&rsquo;. Among our page builder features are: Box Shadows, Background Overlays, Hover Effects, Headline Effects, Animations, Shape Dividers, Gradient Backgrounds and much more.</p>\n<h4>Pre-Designed Templates &amp; Blocks</h4>\n<p>Choose from 100+ of beautiful full page <a href=\"https://library.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WordPress templates</a> and customize them to make them your own. You can also build your page by choosing from 300+ Blocks.</p>\n<p>Blocks are pre-designed section templates that can be easily combined into any page. Blocks include a variety of categories: services, testimonials, call to action and more. Save and reuse Elementor templates on different pages, or export them to a different website with a click.</p>\n<h4>Mobile First. Mobile Editing.</h4>\n<p>Elementor Page Builder comes with an exclusive toolset, that lets you create truly a responsive website in a whole new and visual way. From different font size, padding and margin per device, to reverse column ordering, this is the most powerful mobile page builder for creating perfect responsive websites.</p>\n<h4>Undo / Redo &amp; Revision History.</h4>\n<p>Our page builder includes undo and redo for any action you make. Click on Ctrl / Cmd + Z, or browse through the complete list of actions. Want to go back ever further? Switch to Revisions to view a complete list of all earlier saved versions of the page.</p>\n<h4>Canvas. Un modèle de page vierge pour les pages d&rsquo;atterrissage.</h4>\n<p>Design your entire page in the page builder. No header, no footer, just Elementor. This is perfect for landing pages and coming soon pages. Canvas works on any theme, and lets you get rid of the header area so you get a blank template to work on.</p>\n<h4>Modes maintenance &#038; en construction intégrés.</h4>\n<p>Need to get your site offline for maintenance? Use Elementor page builder&rsquo;s built in Maintenance Mode &amp; Coming Soon feature to show your visitors an under construction / coming soon page.</p>\n<h4>Esayez Elementor Pro. Le meilleur constructeur de page pour WordPress.</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://elementor.com/pro/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Pro</a> améliore considérablement votre flux de travail de conception et vous permet de concevoir plus rapidement et mieux que jamais. Avec Elementor Pro, tout se fait visuellement et sans code.</p>\n<p>Making changes to your theme shouldn&rsquo;t be so hard. Endless coding, dealing with developers, switching themes. The <a href=\"https://elementor.com/theme-builder/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Theme Builder</a> in Elementor Pro turns the entire process of creating WordPress websites 100% visual including your site&rsquo;s header, footer, single post and archive page design.</p>\n<p>Il existe de nombreuses autres <a href=\"https://elementor.com/features/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">fonctionnalités</a> pour vous aider à construire de meilleurs sites web :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visual and intuitive form builder</li>\n<li>Marketing automation and CRM integrations</li>\n<li>Polices personnalisées</li>\n<li>Role manager</li>\n<li>Blog post layout widget</li>\n<li>Image &amp; video sliders</li>\n<li>WooCommerce</li>\n<li>Widgets globaux</li>\n<li>CSS personnalisé</li>\n<li>Animated headlines</li>\n<li>Et bien plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Join the elite web professionals who enjoy <a href=\"https://elementor.com/pro/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Pro</a>!</p>\n<h4>30 widgets et décomptes gratuits</h4>\n<p>Nous avons intégré 30 des widgets les plus utiles dans notre constructeur de page. En réalité, c’est bien plus que ce que nous avions à offrir, mais nous ne voulions mettre de côté aucun widget afin que vous puissiez atteindre le sommet de vos capacités de conception.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Titre</strong>. Ajouter un titre attirant.</li>\n<li><strong>Image</strong>. Contrôlez la taille, l&rsquo;opacité et d&rsquo;autres réglages des images.</li>\n<li><strong>Éditeur de texte</strong>. Un éditeur de texte visuel, comme l’éditeur de WordPress.</li>\n<li><strong>Vidéo</strong>. Ajoutez des vidéos YouTube \\ Vimeo dans votre page.</li>\n<li><strong>Bouton</strong>. Contrôlez tous les aspects de la conception du bouton.</li>\n<li><strong>Boîte d’image</strong>. Une boîte qui contient une image, un titre et un texte.</li>\n<li><strong>Témoignages</strong>. Témoignages de clients qui montrent la preuve sociale.</li>\n<li><strong>Icône</strong>. Placez une ou plusieurs des 600+ icônes disponibles.</li>\n<li><strong>Boîte d’icône</strong>. Fonctionne comme la boîte d’images, uniquement avec des icônes.</li>\n<li><strong>Icônes sociales</strong>. Icônes vers vos pages sociales comme Facebook/Twitter.</li>\n<li><strong>Galerie d’images</strong>. Affiche vos images dans une grille alignée.</li>\n<li><strong>Carrousel d’images</strong>. Un carrousel rotatif ou un diaporama des images choisies.</li>\n<li><strong>Liste d’icônes</strong>. Une liste à puces avec n&rsquo;importe quelle icône et texte choisis.</li>\n<li><strong>Compteur</strong>. Afficher des statistiques et des chiffres de façon croissante.</li>\n<li><strong>Barre de progression</strong>. Inclure une barre de progression progressive.</li>\n<li><strong>Tabs</strong>. Vertical or horizontal tabs that display different pieces of content.</li>\n<li><strong>Accordéon</strong>. Un affichage repliable du contenu.</li>\n<li><strong>Basculer</strong>. Comm un accordéon, pour les pages de FAQ.</li>\n<li><strong>Notation par étoiles</strong>. Ajoutez des preuves sociales avec une notation par étoiles stylisée.</li>\n<li><strong>Alerte</strong>. Une boîte d’alerte colorée pour attirer l’attention du visiteur.</li>\n<li><strong>HTML</strong>. Insérez du code dans la page. </li>\n<li><strong>Code court</strong>. Insérez facilement dans la page des codes courts de n’importe quelle extension.</li>\n<li><strong>Ancre de menu</strong>. Lier n’importe quel menu à cette ancre.</li>\n<li><strong>Lire plus</strong>. Définissez la coupure <code>Lire plus</code> pour l’extrait dans les pages d’archive.</li>\n<li><strong>Colonne latérale</strong>. Ajouter une barre colonne dans la page.</li>\n<li><strong>Google Maps</strong>. Intégrer des cartes dans la page.</li>\n<li><strong>SoundCloud</strong>. Ajouter du son depuis SoundCloud.</li>\n<li><strong>Séparateur</strong>. Une ligne pour séparer les différents éléments de la page.</li>\n<li><strong>Espacement</strong>. Un espace qui divise les différents éléments.</li>\n<li><strong>Colonnes</strong>. Créer des colonnes imbriquées dans la colonne.</li>\n<li><strong>Et comptant&#8230;</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Multilingue &amp; RTL pris en charge.</h4>\n<p>We&rsquo;ve integrated RTL and multi language support within the framework of our page builder, so you get a translated panel out of the box, as well as RTL typography support, and developer options to add even more languages.</p>\n<h4>API développeur.</h4>\n<p>Le constructeur de page Elementor est gratuit et open source. C’est l’extension de création de page idéale à étendre et à intégrer davantage. Elle a été créée et développée avec le développeur en tête, et nous avons déjà vu certains modules vraiment remarquables développés.<br />\nPour vous aider à démarrer et à apprendre à intégrer Elementor, nous avons créé les <a href=\"https://developers.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Ressources officielles de développement Elementor </a> et la <a href=\"https://code.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Référence au code</a>.</p>\n<h4>Traductions</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/en-au/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Anglais (Australie)</a> &#8211; (en_AU)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/en-gb/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Anglais (UK)</a> &#8211; (en_GB)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/en-ca/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Anglais (Canada)</a> &#8211; (en_CA)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/fr/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Français</a> &#8211; (fr_FR)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/fr-be/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Français (Belgique)</a> &#8211; (fr_BE)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/de/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Allemand</a> &#8211; (de_DE)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ro/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Roumain</a> &#8211; (ro_RO)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/es/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Espagnol (Espagne)</a> &#8211; (es_ES)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/es-mx/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Espagnol (Mexique)</a> &#8211; (es_MX)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ja/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Japonais</a> &#8211; (ja)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/pt-br/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Portugais (Portugal)</a> &#8211; (pt_PT)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/pt-br/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Portugais (Brésil)</a> &#8211; (pt_BR)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/sv/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Suédois</a> &#8211; (sv_SE)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/nl/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Néerlandais</a> &#8211; (nl_NL)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/da/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Danois</a> &#8211; (da_DK)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/pl/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Polonais</a> &#8211; (pl_PL)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ro/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Roumain</a> &#8211; (ro_RO)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/zh-cn/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Chinois (Chine)</a> &#8211; (zh_CN)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/zh-tw/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Chinois (Taiwan)</a> &#8211; (zh_TW)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/fa/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Persan</a> &#8211; (fa_IR)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/he/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Hébreu</a> &#8211; (he_IL)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ru/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Russe</a> &#8211; (ru_RU)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ro/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Roumain</a> &#8211; (ro_RO) &#8211; en cours</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/bg/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Bulgare</a> &#8211; (hu_HU) &#8211; (bg_BG)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/el/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Grec</a> &#8211; (el)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ca/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Catalan</a> &#8211; (ca)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/cs/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Tchèque</a> &#8211; (cs_CZ)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/hu/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Hongrois</a> &#8211; (hu_HU)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/hr/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Croate</a> &#8211; (hr)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/fi/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Finlandais</a> &#8211; (fi)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/ar/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Arabe</a> &#8211; (ar)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/af/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Afrikaans</a> &#8211; (af)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/locale/uk/default/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Ukrainien</a> &#8211; (uk)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Être un contributeur</h4>\n<p>If you want to contribute, go to our <a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor GitHub Repository</a> and see where you can help.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez également ajouter une nouvelle langue via <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">translate.wordpress.org</a>. Nous avons créé un petit guide explicant <a href=\"https://go.elementor.com/translate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">comment traduire et localiser l’extension</a>.</p>\n<h4>Documentation et support</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Pour de la documentation et des tutoriels, visitez notre <a href=\"https://docs.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">documentation</a>.</li>\n<li>Si vous avez d&rsquo;autres questions, visitez notre page de support sur <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/elementor\">le forum de l’extension</a>.</li>\n<li>Pour plus d&rsquo;informations sur les fonctionnalités, les FAQ et la documentation, consultez notre site internet <a href=\"https://elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Elementor Page Builder</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Vous avez aimé Elementor ?</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Rejoignez notre <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/Elementors/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">groupe Facebook</a>.</li>\n<li>Apprenez via nos tutoriels sur <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/elementor\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">la chaîne Youtube</a>.</li>\n<li>Ou nous évaluer sur <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/elementor/reviews/?filter=5/#new-post\">WordPress</a> 🙂</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:1659:\"<h4>Exigences minimales</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress 5.0 ou supérieur</li>\n<li>PHP version 5.6 ou supérieure</li>\n<li>MySQL version 5.0 ou supérieure</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Nous recommandons que votre serveur supporte :</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>PHP version 7.0 ou supérieure</li>\n<li>MySQL version 5.6 ou supérieure</li>\n<li>WordPress Memory limit of 64 MB or greater (128 MB or higher is preferred)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ypn6fltn_7s?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Installez à l&rsquo;aide de l’installateur d’extension intégré WordPress, ou décompressez le fichier zip et déposez le contenu dans le répertoire <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> de votre installation WordPress.</li>\n<li>Activez l’extension dans le menu « Extensions » de WordPress.</li>\n<li>Allez à Pages &gt; Ajouter une nouvelle</li>\n<li>Appuyez sur le bouton &lsquo;Modifier avec Elementor&rsquo;.</li>\n<li>Vous pouvez maintenant glisser et déposer des widgets du panneau de gauche sur la zone de contenu, aussi bien que d&rsquo;ajouter de nouvelles sections et colonnes qui composent la structure de la page.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Pour de la documentation et des tutoriels, visitez notre <a href=\"https://docs.elementor.com/?utm_source=wp-repo&amp;utm_medium=link&amp;utm_campaign=readme\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">base de connaissance</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:1539:\"\n<h4>With Elementor, do I still need a theme?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes. Think of it like this: a theme is like the frame of the picture, and Elementor is the tool to paint the picture inside the frame.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Is Elementor compatible with Posts and Custom Post Types?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>It sure is! You can set which post types will enable Elementor in the settings page.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I use other plugin widgets inside Elementor?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Tout à fait ! Les widgets qui apparaissent sur la page de widgets WordPress apparaîtront automatiquement dans Elementor. Il vous suffit de les glisser-déposer dans votre page.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Do I need to know how to code to use Elementor?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Absolument pas ! Elementor est un constructeur de page en direct de l’interface utilisateur, qui vous permet d’atteindre une conception haut de gamme sans avoir besoin d’écrire une seule ligne de code ou de CSS.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Will Elementor work with RTL or other languages?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yeah! Elementor enables to seamlessly build RTL pages as well as other translated pages in any language. You can read more about <a href=\"https://go.elementor.com/translate/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">translation and localization</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>My site is working with WordPress 2.6, will Elementor work for me?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Non. Elementor prend en charge WordPress 5.0 ou supérieur et est compatible avec PHP 5.6 ou supérieur. Nous recommandons que votre hébergeur prenne en charge PHP version 7.0 ou supérieure et MySQL version 5.6 ou supérieure.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:186405:\"<h4>2.9.8 &#8211; 2020-04-21</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Added <code>.webp</code> file extension support to Elementor Lightbox</li>\n<li>Fix: Added missing font-family for <code>elementor-button</code> class to avoid system font (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/11166\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#11166</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Site Part without any content has no height and not accessible in some cases</li>\n<li>Fix: PHP notice in Connect module</li>\n<li>Fix: Navigator resize action is not available in edge cases</li>\n<li>Fix: SVG sanitizer <code>href</code> attribute for better security</li>\n<li>Fix: Hardened user role that is allowed to upload unfiltered files for better security</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.7 &#8211; 2020-03-25</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Added compatibility with WordPress v5.4 (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10745\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10745</a>)</li>\n<li>Tweak: Show Typography section to everyone in Section, Column and Inner Section elements (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10592\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10592</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Custom Attributes section missing in Advanced tab (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10881\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10881</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Title color &amp; Typography settings are being overridden by Theme Style in Accordion and Toggle widget (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10900\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10900</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Merged « Play On Mobile » string for better i18n in Video widget (Props <a href=\"https://github.com/pedro-mendonca\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">@pedro-mendonca</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10315\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10315</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Whatsapp share link does not escape HTML entities (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10746\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10746</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Invalid request error conflict with Yoast plugin and Share Buttons widget (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10746\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10746</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: FontAwesome Pro icons not loading in edge cases</li>\n<li>Fix: Missing Dynamic indication in Range control (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10835\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10835</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Carousel spins multiple times when loading in Image Carousel widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Theme style overrides Lightbox Share links color</li>\n<li>Fix: Loading spinner placement glitch in URL control</li>\n<li>Fix: Missing separator control in Icon widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Dynamic Tags with the character “0” are not visible on frontend</li>\n<li>Fix: Dashboard menu UI glitch for non-Administrator role users</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.6 &#8211; 2020-03-12</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Removed redundant dynamic capabilities from all of color controls inside Group controls in Theme Style</li>\n<li>Fix: Global widget is clickable when editing Theme Style</li>\n<li>Fix: Dropcap not working immediately in Text Editor widget</li>\n<li>Security Fix: Enable Safe Mode only for <code>activate_plugins</code> capability</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.5 &#8211; 2020-03-09</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Added new parameter to Swiper wrapper to limit breakpoint intervention (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10525\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10525</a>)</li>\n<li>Tweak: Updated E-Gallery library to v1.1.2</li>\n<li>Tweak: Show descriptive Pro Promotions only for Administrator role</li>\n<li>Fix: Inconsistent responsive display issue in the Editor when using Custom Breakpoints (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10540\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10540</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Editor not loading when the Library launches on load (<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/topic/editor-broken-in-2-9-4/\">Topic</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Gallery Columns does not update immediately in the preview when in Masonry layout</li>\n<li>Fix: Navigator does not update according to the current site part being edited</li>\n<li>Fix: Hidden responsive indicator missing in editor</li>\n<li>Fix: Tabs widget title color not working on mobile</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.4 &#8211; 2020-03-04</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Added support for Elementor Pro v2.9.0</li>\n<li>Tweak: Updated Swiper.js library to v5.3.6</li>\n<li>Tweak: Added version expected release date for Theme Style Custom CSS and Dynamic Color promotions</li>\n<li>Fix: Warning in <code>/base/controls-stack.php</code> when a 3rd party controls doesn’t have a default dynamic value (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10578\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10578</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Alignment issue on drag when not set to Infinite Loop in Image Carousel widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Title Color change both title and link color in Accordion widget</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.3 &#8211; 2020-02-26</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Don&rsquo;t show the « Have a look » link after successful Theme Style publish</li>\n<li>Tweak: Show Database update notice only for users with <code>update_plugins</code> capability</li>\n<li>Tweak: Added Custom CSS promotion section in Theme Style</li>\n<li>Tweak: Added compatibility for Pro v2.9 features</li>\n<li>Fix: Warning in <code>/base/controls-stack.php</code> when a control doesn&rsquo;t have a dynamic capability (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10578\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10578</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Beta Tester sign up modal pops up multiple times after signing up</li>\n<li>Fix: <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> Links appear with <code>underline</code> text-decoration</li>\n<li>Fix: Shortcode doesn&rsquo;t render when exiting inline edit</li>\n<li>Fix: Whatsapp not sharing the link of the page in Share buttons widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Whatsapp share doesn&rsquo;t include line breaks between the page title and the URL in Share buttons widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Box Shadow doesn&rsquo;t display properly in Toggle widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Custom Link Attributes are not being applied in Icon Box widget</li>\n<li>Fix: Added sanitization to Custom Link Attributes control to avoid security issue (Props <a href=\"https://github.com/yzy9951\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">@yzy9951</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.2 &#8211; 2020-02-16</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Responsive issue when using Slides to Show control in carousel widgets (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10540\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10540</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Title and Description causes JS error in Lightbox in edge cases</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.9.1 &#8211; 2020-02-13</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Added Native WordPress Gallery support for lightbox pagination</li>\n<li>Tweak: Updated eicons library to v5.6.2</li>\n<li>Fix: Popup builder not accessible when Pro plugin is active (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10502\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10502</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix: Pagination not working when one item is visible in carousel widgets (<a href=\"https://github.com/elementor/elementor/issues/10508\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">#10508</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress