\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nstone01\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/709d0a260b8dbc37e477fe3215e3cd06?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/709d0a260b8dbc37e477fe3215e3cd06?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nstone01\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nstone01</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Not only is the product great, but the support is amazing. Thanks Jamie for all your help</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">They see mistakes that you might not</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scaramia\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0815d34f32b04480d72672c601636bb1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0815d34f32b04480d72672c601636bb1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/scaramia\" class=\"reviewer-name\">scaramia</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 10, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">...and then you can fix it, and learn something.  Win Win!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">BEST IN CLASS, PERIOD!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thegutelife\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/066c1563ac5b7af4f5b7e98833009c31?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/066c1563ac5b7af4f5b7e98833009c31?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thegutelife\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thegutelife</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">avril 7, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using BB for 5 years and have had nothing but an exceptional experience. Their drag and drop interface is amazing, their customer support is EXACTLY what you\'re looking for- always responsive, no issue too small or too big, and they ALWAYS solve it.\n\nIf you\'re looking to really learn how to build websites or run an advertising / media / marketing agency that builds websites, BB TOTALLY is what you need.\n\nThanks again guys! You all rock!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brandontan903\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73b8bddbf4abdb30268efe3709987a0b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/73b8bddbf4abdb30268efe3709987a0b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brandontan903\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brandontan903</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It is so great until I have no word to say</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesomely Unparalleled</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m4cl4rkgmailcom\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0b6c9344d910f426f882bcf20fc40da5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0b6c9344d910f426f882bcf20fc40da5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m4cl4rkgmailcom\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cl4rk <small>(m4cl4rk@gmail.com)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">When you come across a product that really resonates, you can feel how much thoughtfulness and love go into making it great and keeping it great. That\'s the feeling you get with BeaverBuilder. Not only is it among the most well-crafted systems you\'ll ever use, it\'s also one of the most delightful.\n\nNo matter the project, I look forward to using this one each and every day.\n\nI don\'t often review things, and when I do, it\'s because the product and/or service really strike me as so extraordinary, that I\'d better chip my two cents in and add my voice to the chorus of happy customers. The product and the customer service here are awesomely unparalleled. In a good way. The best way. :)\n\nThanks, Builder Team. You rock.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Invaluable</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryan-freedman\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46b03926f7c0569a4fa04846a428c233?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46b03926f7c0569a4fa04846a428c233?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bryan-freedman\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Bryan Freedman</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">mars 5, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">For beginner/wannabe web designers like me, this is a must. Makes designing pages so much easier. Great templates too. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Product and Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/klhall1987\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27a47a338f432fdfd9fa2531f50401ff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27a47a338f432fdfd9fa2531f50401ff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/klhall1987\" class=\"reviewer-name\">klhall1987</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 12, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This product is amazing. I seriously can\'t sing it\'s praises enough. I use it on most sites I build at this point, it makes spinning up a site super simple and their support team is incredible. They always seem to go the extra mile. If you\'re look for a page builder, this is the place start and end your search! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Not overly impressed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/krammig\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb6ea68f3d897997ad1ded10271205ad?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fb6ea68f3d897997ad1ded1027120